
               F/WIN ANTI-VIRUS PRICING/ORDERING INFORMATION
               =============================================


There are different order files to use depending upon how you
wish to have F/WIN Anti-Virus shipped to you.  



                              OPTION #1
                              =========

To have it sent to you by PGP ASCII armor in an e-mail message:
                          ------------------------------------

    ORDR_PGP.DOC   -  instructions for form in ORDR_PGP.TXT
    ORDR_PGP.TXT   -  Actual order form




                             OPTION #2
                             =========

To have it sent to you in a UUENCODED, Password protected PKZIP
                            ----------------------------------- 
file in an e-mail message:

    ORDRPKZP.DOC   -  instructions for form in ORDRPKZP.TXT
    ORDRPKZP.TXT   -  Actual order form




